{"tid":552641,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"身為男人覺得自己好廢","createTime":"2018-02-06T16:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T18:47:58.000Z","uid":42419,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a749bccca3f8adc1dbe9d6c5850c875993317da","tid":552641,"uid":42419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"唔靚仔 運動唔掂 打機唔掂<br />\n除咗讀書叻啲無可取嘅地方<br />\n喺女朋友啲朋友嘅男友面前無地自容<br />\n搞到女友咩面都冇曬<br />\n<br />\n最痛心係女友完全唔介意 無嫌棄自己<br />\n轉個頭係咁讚自己有幾好<br />\n仲暗地裏幫自己講好說話<br />\n<br />\n依世人最驕傲就係同到佢拍拖<br />\n但有時真係覺得自己咁廢配唔起咁好嘅女仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab97e9ce0a2be5a8053515febceb5026bb2cb6d2","tid":552641,"uid":142758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"有女朋友都唔算廢吖<br />\n巴打有無問過佢鍾意你啲咩啊其實 你講到自己咁廢"},{"pid":"d75ab0d6613ea9b36afed630e66459dabf5b3754","tid":552641,"uid":102609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"咁我呢啲連女都溝唔到嘅咪仲廢<br />\n<br />\n巴打比啲自信自己<br />\n<br />\n超碼仲有人係愛你先"},{"pid":"3570ff055e8992c7a16115dc00bec41f976cc597","tid":552641,"uid":165864,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"女仔一定係覺得你好先同你一齊<br />\n可能有啲你自己不以為意嘅嘢對佢黎講係好大嘅優點<br />\n例如：孝順、專一、脾氣好"},{"pid":"593d469fc6ae8f8d28f0fac4fea0c6591e1f59f7","tid":552641,"uid":95499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"兜咁大個圈想曬自己有女<br />\n<br />\n潛台詞：我呢d廢人都有女呀，咁你地班連登仔係咩就自己諗啦"},{"pid":"91755bd3bded1893ec553a3a4579f544efcae2eb","tid":552641,"uid":51134,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:48:53.000Z","msg":"你廢在唔識知足。"},{"pid":"577b05a3fc532fedf71eb1a81c2853272f4add3c","tid":552641,"uid":68047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T16:51:53.000Z","msg":